creator: UKGames
descriptionHtml:
This Zigzag mix game is very easy to play; Just touch anywhere on the screen and let your character change direction. Remember to draw zigzags while playing. When you travel with your character, you will never fall down if you change direction in time. Don't forget to eat the delicious food that comes in front of you, so you can keep your energy high and run faster. Zigzag game will accelerate gradually. If you direct your character well, it will never fall to the ground. Let's see how long you can hold him without falling down?

How to play:

1) Change the direction of the curves to make your character fall down.
2) On the way you must eat the fruits that come before you and use it to change your character when it comes to a certain number. So the zigzag mix game gives you more points
3) You get more points in two ways.
1. If you play with the new characters you get, the points in the game are multiplied by an extra coefficient. So you get more points. This is necessary to get to the top.
2. Or you should go very far without dropping your character down.
4) Never give up trying! Eat your fruit and move forward!

3) You get more points in two ways.
1. You have to play with the new characters you get! Thus, your points will be multiplied by a higher coefficient and you will earn more points. This is necessary for you to rise to the top.
2. Or you have to go far without falling down with your character.
4) Never stop trying! Eat your fruits and move forward!
